<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qml-qtgamepad-gamepadmanager.xml">GamepadManager</db:link> QML type provides a high-level interface for querying the attached gamepads and events related to all of the connected devices.</db:para>
</db:section>
